      "description": "## What's changed\r\n\r\nThis is a patch release fixing issues flagged during the Obsidian plugin review.\r\n\r\n### Fixes\r\n- Bumped `minAppVersion` to `1.7.2` to match the APIs actually used by the plugin\r\n- Replaced bare `setTimeout` calls with `window.setTimeout` for popout window compatibility\r\n- Removed a redundant type assertion in the view layer\r\n- Replaced `!important` overrides in CSS with higher-specificity selectors\r\n\r\n### Housekeeping\r\n- UI button labels updated to sentence case per Obsidian style guidelines\r\n- `CONTRIBUTING.md` corrected: sentence case rule, minimum Obsidian version, full src file list\r\n- `README.md` corrected: button label typo fixed\r\n\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/aadityaincode/Deep-Notes/compare/1.1.0...1.1.1",
