      "description": "## What's New in 1.1.0\r\n\r\n### Visual Overhaul\r\n- Full purple theme with a pill-based mode switcher\r\n- Improved button sizing and layout across all modes\r\n- Mode-specific \"How It Works\" guide for each study mode\r\n\r\n### Flashcards\r\n- 3D click-to-flip card animation\r\n- Export to Markdown button properly surfaced\r\n\r\n### Session Management\r\n- Per-mode session state: switching modes no longer loses your progress\r\n- Background generation: switch modes freely while content loads\r\n\r\n### Under the Hood\r\n- TypeScript target bumped to ES2019\r\n- Author updated to Eidos\r\n",
